### Skills adapted from wondelai/skills

The following skills in this plugin were copied from wondelai/skills
(commit 4d322538be8b9ce98fca29b0eef26d67bff1fe82, 2026-04-05) with the
following modifications only: (1) frontmatter `name` field shortened for
plugin namespace integration, (2) attribution footer appended to each
SKILL.md. No semantic changes to content or structure.

| Plugin path | Original wondelai skill |
|---|---|
| `skills/systems/refactoring/` | `refactoring-ui` |
| `skills/systems/typography/` | `web-typography` |
| `skills/audit/heuristics/` | `ux-heuristics` |
| `skills/audit/cro/` | `cro-methodology` |
| `skills/interaction/microinteractions/` | `microinteractions` |
| `skills/behavior/hooked/` | `hooked-ux` |
| `skills/behavior/retention/` | `improve-retention` |
| `skills/behavior/copy/` | `made-to-stick` |
